  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether in pre-hypertensive and hypertensive states
      such as white coat hypertension, obesity related hypertension or resistant hypertension,
      renal function is more sensitive to orthostatic stress.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
